Script Name: getLocationsForAddVariety
Excel Columns: Location,Output

Step 1 [LOGIC]:
  - Logic: Extracts address text or lat/lng from input row, case-insensitively.

Step 2 [API]:
  - Step/Variable Name: Google Geocode API Call
  - Call GET https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/geocode/json
  - Payload Type: QUERY
  - Payload Example: { "address": "<address_text_from_input>", "latlng": "<lat_from_input>,<lng_from_input>", "key": "<GOOGLE_API_KEY>" }
  - Expected Response: address_info
  - Instructions: Calls Google Geocode API using country from input.

Step 3 [LOGIC]:
  - Logic: Parses Google Geocode API response, extracts components, and updates output row as below payload structure
